                '_ar_when_to_call'   => 'Thermocouple replacement is a straightforward professional repair. Our technician replaces the failed thermocouple with a genuine Viking OEM component matched to the burner position on your specific cooktop model.',
                '_ar_cost_range'     => '$110 – $240',
