            'meta_title' => 'Viking Induction Cooktop Not Detecting Pan — Cookware Detection Fault',
            'meta_desc'  => 'Viking induction cooktop not recognizing cookware or displaying a no-pan error? Learn the causes of pan detection failure and when service is needed.',
